<link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.1.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<div class="container">
  <img src="https://megodating.com/assets/dist/img/mego.png" class="mt-3 mb-3 logo">
  
  <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 order-md-last">
         
  <h1 class="headline" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 2.3rem; line-height: 1.22; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Condensed&quot;, &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Community Guidelines</h1><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Welcome to the Mego community. If you’re honest, kind and respectful to others, you’ll always be welcome here. If you choose not to be, you may not last. Our goal is to allow users to express themselves freely as long as it doesn’t offend others. Everyone is held to the same standard on Mego. We’re asking you to be considerate, think before you act, and abide by our community guidelines both on and offline. You heard that right: your offline behavior can lead to termination of your Mego account.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Below is a list of our community policies. If you violate any of these policies, you might be banned from Mego. Seriously, don’t make us Swipe Left on you—because there will be no do-overs once we do. We encourage you to&nbsp;<a href="https://www.help.Mego.com/hc/en-us/articles/115003359426-How-do-I-report-someone" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--color--text-link,inherit); text-decoration-line: underline;">report</a>&nbsp;any behavior that violates our policies, and read up on our&nbsp;<a href="https://policies.Mego.com/safety" style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--color--text-link,inherit); text-decoration-line: underline;">Safety Tips</a>.</p><h2 style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 1rem 0px 0.8rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.22; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Condensed&quot;, &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Mego is not for:</h2><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Nudity/Sexual Content</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">We’re not asking you to comb your hair to one side or even speak in full sentences; but please keep it classy and appropriate for public consumption. No nudity, no sexually explicit content, and don’t chronicle all of your sexual desires in your bio. Keep it clean.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Harassment</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Do not engage, or encourage others to engage, in any targeted abuse or harassment against any other user. This includes sending any unsolicited sexual content to your matches. Reports of stalking, threats, bullying, or intimidation, are taken very seriously.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Violence and Physical Harm</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">We do not tolerate violent, graphic, or gory content on Mego, or any actions or content that advocate for or threaten violence of any sort, including threatening or promoting terrorism. Physical assault, coercion, and any acts of violence are strictly prohibited.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Content that advocates for or glorifies suicide or self-harm is also not allowed. In these situations, we may take a number of steps to assist the user, including reaching out with crisis resources.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Hate Speech</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Any content that promotes, advocates for, or condones racism, bigotry, hatred, or violence against individuals or groups based on factors like (but not limited to) race, ethnicity, religious affiliation, disability, gender, age, national origin, sexual orientation, or gender identity is not allowed.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Private Information</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Don’t publicly broadcast any private information, yours or anyone else’s. This includes social security numbers, passports, passwords, financial information or unlisted contact information, such as phone numbers, email addresses, home/work address.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Spam</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Don’t be fake. Be real instead. Don’t use Mego to drive people to external websites via a link or otherwise.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Promotion or Solicitation</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Soliciting other users is prohibited on Mego. It’s fine to invite your matches to something that you’re doing, but if the purpose of your profile is to advertise your event or business, non-profit, political campaign, contest, or to conduct research, we may delete your account. While we’re excited that you’re doing a comedy show next week, please don’t use Mego to promote it.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Prostitution and Trafficking</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Promoting or advocating for commercial sexual services, human trafficking or other non-consensual sexual acts is strictly prohibited and will result in your account being banned from Mego.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Scamming</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Mego has a zero-tolerance policy on predatory behavior of any kind. Anyone attempting to get other users’ private information for fraudulent or illegal activity may be banned. Any user caught sharing their own financial account information (PayPal, Venmo, etc.) for the purpose of receiving money from other users may also be banned from Mego.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Impersonation</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Be yourself! Don’t pretend to be someone else.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Do not impersonate, or otherwise misrepresent affiliation, connection or association with, any person or entity. This includes parody accounts. While we think your Mike Pence profile is hilarious, you aren’t Mike Pence. And if you are, what are you doing on Mego?</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Minors</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">You must be 18 years of age or older to use Mego. As such, we do not allow images of unaccompanied minors. If you want to post photos of your children, please make sure that you are in the photo as well. If you see a profile that includes an unaccompanied minor, encourages harm to a minor, or depicts a minor in a sexual or suggestive way, please report it immediately.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Copyright and Trademark Infringement</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">If it’s not yours, don’t post it. If your Mego profile includes any work that is copyrighted or trademarked by others, don’t display it, unless you are allowed to do so.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Illegal Usage</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Don’t use Mego to do anything illegal. If it’s illegal IRL, it’s illegal on Mego.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">One Person, One Account</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Mego accounts cannot have multiple owners, so don’t create an account with your friend or significant other. Additionally, please don’t maintain multiple Mego accounts.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Third Party Apps</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">The use of any apps created by anyone other than Mego that claim to offer our service or unlock special Mego features (like auto-swipers) is not allowed.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Account Dormancy</span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0.8rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 17.3333px; line-height: 1.47; font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(80, 89, 101);">Mego is fun to use... all the time! Use Mego at the lake, use Mego while eating cake. Use Mego when you’re out, use Mego when in doubt! But, if you don’t log in to your Mego account in 2 years, we may delete your account for inactivity.</p><div><br></div>
   
